#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.ravel"
msgstr "# triton.language.ravel"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:4
msgid "将输入张量展平为一维张量，保持元素在内存中的顺序，输出张量的总元素数与输入张量相同。"
msgstr "Flatten the input tensor into a one-dimensional tensor, preserving the order of elements in memory. The total number of elements in the output tensor is the same as that of the input tensor."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.ravel(input)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.ravel()` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.ravel(input)` - function call form\n"
"- `input.ravel()` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Features:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:12
msgid ""
"- 将输入张量展平为一维张量\n"
"- 保持元素在内存中的顺序\n"
"- 输出张量的总元素数与输入张量相同\n"
msgstr ""
"- Flatten the input tensor into a one-dimensional tensor\n"
"- Preserve the order of elements in memory\n"
"- The total number of elements in the output tensor is the same as that of the input tensor\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

