"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|----------|-------------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/ravel.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 一维张量，包含输入张量的所有元素\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 按行优先顺序展平\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** 1D tensor containing all elements of the input tensor\n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Memory layout:** Flattened in row-major order\n"

